      "description": "Offered is an exceptional specimen of the E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is in true collector condition, boasting a factory-original finish with zero paint correction required. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach: the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC Motorsports coated shells and ARP hardware. The 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile shifts through a short-throw linkage into a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and showing zero bushing deflection. No weeping from the valve covers or oil pan. This is a turnkey, high-performance machine for the discerning purist who values mechanical integrity and archival preservation.",
